{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens"}]},{"text":" for components with a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"control item","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"ControlItemComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{